Introduction
============

A module to calculate the similarity of a pair of strings, and to look
up similar strings in a dictionary-like structure. Inspired by Perl's
String::Trigram.

Homepage: http://python-ngram.sourceforge.net/

Installation
============

Install in /usr/local::

  python setup.py --prefix=/usr/local

Just link to this source directory so code can be edited here::

  ./setup.py develop --prefix=/usr/local


Usage
=====

>>> from ngram import ngram
>>> help(ngram)


API Documentation
=================

Run::

 epydoc -v ngram.py

To generate API documentation in ./html/index.html

See http://epydoc.sourceforge.net/


